[Although EEE is not responsible for massive and widespread epidemics, the
high mortality rate associated with this disease and its annual occurrence
along the eastern seaboard of the U.S. make this a serious illness.
Apparently, a "Distant Early Warning" system had been put in place but the
message might not have gotten to everyone; pity. On the brighter side,
consider all the people who have not contracted this illness because they are
taking adequate precautions. -- Mod CHC]
